## Session Startup Protocol

**Every time a new session starts or before working on any task:**

1. Read this file (CLAUDE.md)
2. Check current task status at `___` (e.g., docs/todo.md, TASKS.md)
3. Read the relevant plan doc(s) for the current task if applicable
4. Do NOT re-implement or duplicate work that is already marked as completed
5. If a task is partially done, pick up where it left off
6. **Always update the task tracker** when completing tasks, discovering blockers, or adding new work

