## After Completing a Task

<!-- Delete this comment: This section tells Claude what to do when it finishes work.
     Without it, Claude often stops without updating tracking files or running tests. -->

1. **Update the task tracker** — mark items complete in your task file (e.g., docs/todo.md)
2. **Update status doc** (if you have one) — reflect the new state of the feature/phase
3. **Run tests** — all tests must pass before marking a task as complete
4. **Run linter/static analysis** (if applicable) — catch issues before commit
